---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import '../styles/global.css';
---

<BaseLayout title="About" description="About SaaSStatsHub — your trusted source for comprehensive SaaS statistics and data.">
  <div class="max-w-[740px] mx-auto px-6 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6">About SaaSStatsHub</h1>

    <div class="space-y-6 text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
      <p>
        <strong class="text-text">SaaSStatsHub</strong> is the #1 source for SaaS statistics and data. We provide comprehensive, up-to-date, and always-cited statistics covering the entire SaaS ecosystem — from market size and growth to adoption rates, pricing trends, and regional insights.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-text">Our Mission</h2>
      <p>
        We believe that reliable data should be accessible to everyone. Whether you're a founder building a business case, an analyst writing a report, or a marketer creating content, SaaSStatsHub gives you the numbers you need — with sources you can trust.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-text">What Makes Us Different</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
        <li><strong class="text-text">Always Cited</strong> — Every data point links back to its original source. No phantom numbers.</li>
        <li><strong class="text-text">Always Current</strong> — We update our statistics regularly to reflect the latest available data.</li>
        <li><strong class="text-text">Comprehensive</strong> — From market size to user growth, we cover every angle of the SaaS industry.</li>
        <li><strong class="text-text">Free</strong> — All our statistics are freely accessible. No paywalls, no subscriptions.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-text">Coverage Areas</h2>
      <p>We cover statistics across all major SaaS categories:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1">
        <li><a href="/categories/crm/" class="text-primary hover:underline">CRM</a> — Salesforce, HubSpot, Zoho, and more</li>
        <li><a href="/categories/marketing/" class="text-primary hover:underline">Marketing</a> — Mailchimp, Hootsuite, and marketing automation</li>
        <li><a href="/categories/ecommerce/" class="text-primary hover:underline">E-commerce</a> — Shopify, WooCommerce, and digital commerce</li>
        <li><a href="/categories/project-management/" class="text-primary hover:underline">Project Management</a> — Asana, Monday.com, Trello</li>
        <li><a href="/categories/hr/" class="text-primary hover:underline">HR</a> — Workday, BambooHR, and HR tech</li>
        <li><a href="/categories/analytics/" class="text-primary hover:underline">Analytics</a> — Tableau, Looker, and business intelligence</li>
        <li><a href="/categories/security/" class="text-primary hover:underline">Security</a> — CrowdStrike, Okta, and cybersecurity</li>
        <li><a href="/categories/communication/" class="text-primary hover:underline">Communication</a> — Slack, Zoom, Microsoft Teams</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-text">Contact</h2>
      <p>
        Have a question, correction, or suggestion? We'd love to hear from you.
        Reach out at <a href="mailto:hello@saasstatshub.com" class="text-primary hover:underline">hello@saasstatshub.com</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
